{"tid":737392,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想報名入樹仁可以黎睇睇","createTime":"2018-07-11T00:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T09:35:16.000Z","uid":194268,"like":19,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe8ee6240f112a658312f99cae74332dba0301d","tid":737392,"uid":194268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:21:43.000Z","msg":"到時收到成績單，去北角寶馬山樹仁大學拎籌 ，大概排一兩個鐘拎完籌之後交form，咁記得拎學生相，同埋個度rlg5有得用八達通影印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 交form就要去禮堂交表同埋交錢 (二百三百到)。交表要大概一個鐘到，因為要俾註冊處d阿嬸登記 。佢地唔太識電腦架，所以要等佢地幫你手寫登記同寫收據俾你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n但係記得要比D耐性，記得帶個尿袋玩手機，順便睇下D環境點，之後阿嬸會安排一個時間叫你去面試 ，到時等信。真係唔識就問student helper<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽講今年helper唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果對輔導及心理學系有興趣，大家黎報名記得冧下係想報讀輔導工作，定係讀純心理學系呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但祝大家入到八大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔駛對住D雞脾櫈"},{"pid":"6daff1fe50cc9ae43a08efac2ffb18513c152585","tid":737392,"uid":163954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbeb71d47459ec7d6874a819961030e069704dc","tid":737392,"uid":194268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51dbc759a09422fdc1af71d2d2e0e10cfaed61b","tid":737392,"uid":194268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:57:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8c043c6b5022bfd9a4e5b9aa39d225f3bad2ac8","tid":737392,"uid":194268,"like